    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">arius</ex></expan> Rustic<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">arius</ex></expan> Pisoni<lb break="no" n="3"/>anus <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">ariae</ex></expan> Cetegianae <lb n="4"/>sorori su<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>bene merenti <lb n="6"/>de suo fecerunt
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Cupa mit Libationsöffnung. Inschriftenfeld beiderseits von geschwungenen Linien flankiert. Text 1 steht über dem Inschriftenfeld. Z. 3: die letzten beiden Buchstaben stehten außerhalb des Inschriftenfeldes. Z. 2-4: statt M(arius/a?) auch M(inicius/a?) denkbar.</p>
            </div>
